{"type":"message","id":"2b86d2cd","parentId":"fa2ebfac","timestamp":"2026-03-21T15:30:42.704Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"啊，出现了一个权限问题。错误说：\n\"Session send visibility is restricted. Set tools.sessions.visibility=all to allow cross-agent access.\"\n\n这说明 `tools.sessions.visibility` 默认是 `tree`（只看到自己的 session 和子 agent），如果要跨 agent 访问其他 agent 的 sessions，需要设置为 `all`。\n\n让我更新配置，添加 `tools.sessions.visibility = \"all\"`。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"需要调整配置！当前 `sessions` 工具的可见性限制了跨 agent 访问。让我更新配置："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_EdhOeptTQrmjMEJEY41JFqmn","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/openclaw.json","old_string":"  \"tools\": {\n    \"agentToAgent\":{\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"allow\":[\"demo\", \"main\"]\n    },\n    \"profile\": \"full\",","new_string":"  \"tools\": {\n    \"sessions\": {\n      \"visibility\": \"all\"\n    },\n    \"agentToAgent\":{\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"allow\":[\"demo\", \"main\", \"wechat-assistant\", \"coder\"]\n    },\n    \"profile\": \"full\","}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":741,"output":260,"cacheRead":33792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34793,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774107035867}}
