{"type":"message","id":"61a6bd87","parentId":"131f0f53","timestamp":"2026-03-21T15:54:41.822Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"消息已发送。现在让我检查是否有来自 demo 机器人的回复。但因为我无法直接接收群里的消息，我需要让用户确认是否收到了 demo 机器人的回复。\n\n或者，我可以尝试通过 sessions 查看 demo agent 是否有新的 session 活动。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"消息已发送！\n\n---\n\n## 等待 Demo 机器人回复\n\n✅ **Main 机器人** 已在群里发送消息（Message ID: `om_x100b54dfbd533ca0c313e6edeca53ce`）\n\n现在需要确认 **Demo 机器人** 是否：\n1. 收到了群消息\n2. 能够回复到群里\n\n---\n\n**请帮我确认：**\n\n1. **Demo 机器人是否在群里显示了这条消息？**\n2. **Demo 机器人是否回复了？**\n\n如果 Demo 机器人没有自动回复，可能是因为：\n- Demo agent 当前没有在运行（没有活跃的 session）\n- Demo agent 的飞书配置需要调整\n\n让我检查一下 Demo agent 当前是否有活跃的 session："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_St95dxKzXMFTpuWH18BLvkOr","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw agents list --bindings 2>/dev/null || echo \"检查 agent 状态...\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":426,"output":242,"cacheRead":47872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48540,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774108474094}}
