ealth: openclaw channels status --probe."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6288,"aggregated":"API Key: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\nAuth Token: sk-kimi-Y311pdLbY8kXigdqhyjfKBjhNdzl4WRzJFderDmHC8eLPhwJMrTmSuG5e8jeaqND\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_doc: Registered feishu_doc, feishu_app_scopes[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_chat: Registered feishu_chat tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_wiki: Registered feishu_wiki tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_drive: Registered feishu_drive tool[39m\n[35m[plugins][39m [36mfeishu_bitable: Registered bitable tools[39m\nAgents:\n- main (default)\n  Workspace: ~/.openclaw/workspace\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/main/agent\n  Model: kimi-coding/k2p5\n  Routing rules: 1\n  Routing: Feishu main\n  Providers:\n    - Feishu main: configured\n  Routing rules:\n    - feishu accountId=main\n- demo\n  Workspace: ~/.openclaw/workspace-demo\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/demo/agent\n  Model: kimi-coding/k2p5\n  Routing rules: 1\n  Routing: Feishu demo\n  Providers:\n    - Feishu demo: configured\n  Routing rules:\n    - feishu accountId=demo\n- wechat-assistant\n  Workspace: ~/.openclaw/workspace-wechat-assistant\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/wechat-assistant/agent\n  Model: kimi-coding/k2p5\n  Routing rules: 1\n  Routing: Feishu wechat-assistant\n  Providers:\n    - Feishu wechat-assistant: configured\n  Routing rules:\n    - feishu accountId=wechat-assistant\n- coder\n  Workspace: ~/.openclaw/workspace-coder\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/coder/agent\n  Model: kimi-coding/k2p5\n  Routing rules: 1\n  Routing: Feishu coder\n  Providers:\n    - Feishu coder: configured\n  Routing rules:\n    - feishu accountId=coder\nRouting rules map channel/account/peer to an agent. Use --bindings for full rules.\nChannel status reflects local config/creds. For live health: openclaw channels status --probe.","cwd":"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"t