{"type":"message","id":"c9ef1f3f","parentId":"96c8d0a2","timestamp":"2026-03-21T15:55:06.276Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！我看到了关键信息：\n\n1. **Main agent 已经在群 `oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e` 的 session**：`agent:main:feishu:group:oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e` (Session ID: 6937afa5-9ef4-4e7d-a8fa-35da2462e955)\n\n2. **Demo agent 也有同一个群的 session**：`agent:demo:feishu:group:oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e` (Session ID: a6b7f984-d070-483f-ad48-465a7d8e0aee)\n\n两个 agent 都有群的 session，说明它们都应该能收到群消息。但是 demo agent 的 session 最后更新时间比较早（1773995720848），可能没有被触发。\n\n让我尝试用 sessions_send 直接给 demo agent 的群 session 发送消息，看看能否通信。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"太好了！发现了关键信息：\n\n✅ **两个 agent 都有群的 session！**\n\n| Agent | 群 Session Key | 状态 |\n|-------|---------------|------|\n| **main** | `agent:main:feishu:group:oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e` | ✅ 活跃 |\n| **demo** | `agent:demo:feishu:group:oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e` | ✅ 存在 |\n\n两个机器人都有群的 session，说明它们都能收到群消息！\n\n---\n\n## 测试：直接用 sessions_send 给 Demo 的群 session 发消息"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_sfJjM3n6LOfW4XfpAtesGrD8","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"message":"🤖 你好！我是 main agent。这是通过 sessions_send 直接发送给你的群 session 的测试消息。\n\n如果你能收到并处理这条消息，说明两个 agent 通过飞书群 + sessions 的通信链路完全正常！\n\n请回复确认，我们可以进一步交流。","sessionKey":"agent:demo:feishu:group:oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e","timeoutSeconds":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":4271,"output":493,"cacheRead":49152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53916,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774108493541}}
