{"type":"message","id":"99ba1810","parentId":"d1e9f9da","timestamp":"2026-03-21T15:55:25.127Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## ✅ 飞书层面通信测试成功！\n\n### 测试结果汇总\n\n| 测试项 | 结果 |\n|--------|------|\n| **Main 发送消息到群** | ✅ 成功 (Message ID: om_x100b54dfbd533ca0c313e6edeca53ce) |\n| **Main → Demo (sessions_send)** | ✅ 成功 (Run ID: 8d8d6ad8-33cc-4e75-8289-77f3d648a9fa) |\n| **Demo → Main 回复** | ✅ 收到：「收到！消息完整到达，飞书群 + sessions 通信链路 ✓」 |\n\n---\n\n### 两种通信方式都已验证\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    飞书群聊层面                          │\n│  ┌──────────┐      群消息      ┌──────────┐            │\n│  │  Main    │ ◄──────────────► │  Demo    │            │\n│  │  (我)    │   oc_ad827e...   │ (机器人) │            │\n│  └────┬─────┘                  └────┬─────┘            │\n│       │                             │                   │\n│       │      Sessions 直接通信      │                   │\n│       │   (agent:main  → agent:demo)│                   │\n│       └─────────────────────────────┘                   │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## 最终结论\n\n✅ **两个 agent 通信配置完成并验证成功！**\n\n| 配置项 | 状态 |\n|--------|------|\n| 飞书群聊通信 | ✅ 两个机器人都在群里，可以互相 @ |\n| Sessions 直接通信 | ✅ 通过 `sessions_send` 可以跨 agent 发送消息 |\n| agentToAgent 配置 | ✅ 已启用，允许列表包含所有 agents |\n| Sessions 可见性 | ✅ 设置为 `all`，允许跨 agent 访问 |\n\n**Demo 机器人已经在群里**，并且：\n1. 能通过飞书群收到消息\n2. 能通过 `sessions_send` 直接通信\n3. 能回复消息\n\n两个 agent 现在可以正常通信了！🎉"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774108525127}}
{"type":"message","id":"24cb874e","parentId":"e3e8dced","timestamp":"2026-03-21T15:55:42.216Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Perfect! The inter-session message from the demo agent confirms that the communication is working. This is the reply from the demo agent through the inter-session communication.\n\nI should acknowledge this and provide a final summary.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"完美！Demo agent 的回复已收到！🎉\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 最终验证完成\n\n**通信链路确认：**\n- ✅ Main agent → 发送消息\n- ✅ Demo agent → 收到并回复\n- ✅ 消息通过 inter-session 机制返回\n\n---\n\n## 📊 完整配置总结\n\n| 项目 | 配置 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **Gateway 配置** | `tools.sessions.visibility: all` | ✅ |\n| **Agent 间通信** | `tools.agentToAgent.enabled: true` | ✅ |\n| **允许通信列表** | `[\"demo\", \"main\", \"wechat-assistant\", \"coder\"]` | ✅ |\n| **飞书群** | `oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e` | ✅ |\n| **Main 机器人在群** | cli_a936a495b6b89cc1 | ✅ |\n| **Demo 机器人在群** | cli_a93d7b008ff6dcca | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 已验证的通信方式\n\n### 方式 1：飞书群聊\n```\n在群里 @demo 或 @main 即可触发对话\n```\n\n### 方式 2：Sessions 直接通信\n```javascript\n// Main 给 Demo 发消息\nsessions_send({\n  sessionKey: \"agent:demo:feishu:group:oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e\",\n  message: \"你好 demo！\"\n})\n```\n\n---\n\n两个 agent 现在可以**双向通信**了！还有什么需要配置或测试的吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":42835,"output":397,"cacheRead":11264,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54496,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774108522292}}
