{"type":"message","id":"d8136866","parentId":"42417264","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:25:35.247Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经在群里发送了一条消息给 demo 机器人。现在需要等待 demo 机器人在群里回复。\n\n如果 demo 机器人的配置正确，它应该能在群里看到这条消息，并且回复到群里。\n\n让我等待一下，看看 demo 是否会回复。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"消息已发送到群里！✅\n\n---\n\n现在看群里是否出现这条消息：**\"@demo 你好！这是一条从 main 发到群里的消息...\"**\n\n如果 demo 机器人配置正确，它应该在群里回复。你能看到这条消息吗？demo 有回复吗？\n\n---\n\n**如果 demo 没有回复，可能的原因：**\n1. demo 机器人的飞书账号没有群里读取消息的权限\n2. demo agent 的处理逻辑没有配置为回复到群里\n\n你能确认一下在群里看到这条消息了吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":766,"output":163,"cacheRead":55808,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56737,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774110329179}}
{"type":"message","id":"dc397c4a","parentId":"d8136866","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:44:58.564Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54dff52d5cb0c2d9d3b68e418b9\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-03-22 00:44 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b54dff52d5cb0c2d9d3b68e418b9]\nou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352: 继续验证"}],"timestamp":1774111498559}}
{"type":"message","id":"f82bb0ab","parentId":"dc397c4a","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:45:05.046Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说\"继续验证\"，意味着之前的消息可能在群里不可见或者 demo 没有回复。让我检查一下 demo agent 的配置，看看为什么它没有回复群消息。\n\n问题可能是：\n1. demo agent 的 `requireMention` 设置为 true，但我没有 @ 到正确的格式\n2. demo agent 没有正确处理群消息\n3. demo agent 可能没有活跃的 session 监听群消息\n\n让我尝试用不同的方式触发 demo——直接在群里用更明确的 @，或者检查 demo 的配置。\n\n首先，让我再发一条消息，这次更明确地 @ demo 机器人。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"好的！让我用不同方式继续验证："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_wkEw1VQh4RA8XSKiRZC98Cp2","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"<at id=\"cli_a93d7b008ff6dcca\"></at> 你好 demo！这是第二条测试消息。请回复确认你能收到并处理群消息。如果收到，请直接回复到群里让大家都能看到。","target":"oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"k2p5","usage":{"input":890,"output":216,"cacheRead":55808,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56914,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774111498562}}
