{"type":"message","id":"4edc55b3","parentId":"e81f692f","timestamp":"2026-03-21T16:45:09.304Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool_l7ApBijqjQNCtcBJD1qZgOmh","toolName":"sessions_history","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:demo:feishu:group:oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e\",\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"NO_REPLY\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1774109127722,\n      \"provenance\": {\n        \"kind\": \"inter_session\",\n        \"sourceSessionKey\": \"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\n        \"sourceChannel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"sourceTool\": \"sessions_send\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"The user sent \\\"NO_REPLY\\\" which is a signal that they don't want a response. I should respect that and not reply.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"NO_REPLY\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"kimi-coding\",\n      \"model\": \"k2p5\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1774109127724\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"Agent-to-agent announce step.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1774109137646,\n      \"provenance\": {\n        \"kind\": \"inter_session\",\n        \"sourceSessionKey\": \"agent:main:feishu:group:oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e\",\n        \"sourceChannel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"sourceTool\": \"sessions_send\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"这是agent-to-agent的announce step，但根据上下文，main agent刚刚发送了NO_REPLY，说明它没有什么要说的。我也不需要说什么，应该回复ANNOUNCE_SKIP。\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"ANNOUNCE_SKIP\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"kimi-coding\",\n      \"model\": \"k2p5\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1774109137648\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"（无回复，通信测试已完成）\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1774109152187,\n      \"provenance\": {\n        \"kind\": \"inter_session\",\n        \"sourceSessionKey\": \"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352\",\n        \"sourceChannel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"sourceTool\": \"sessions_send\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"用户用中文说\\\"无回复，通信测试已完成\\\"，这看起来像是main agent的状态更新或结束语。既然测试已经完成，我不需要再回复什么特别的内容，可以简单确认一下或者保持沉默。\\n\\n根据AGENTS.md的指导，在群聊中：\\n- 如果对话已经自然结束，不需要强行回复\\n- 如果已经有人（或agent）总结了情况，不需要重复\\n\\n这里main agent已经说了\\\"通信测试已完成\\\"，我觉得可以简单回一个确认或者表情，表示收到了。但也可以NO_REPLY，因为这是一个状态声明而不是需要回复的问题。\\n\\n我选择简单回复表示收到。\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"收到 👍 测试圆满完成！\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"kimi-coding\",\n      \"model\": \"k2p5\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1774109152189\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"用户正在测试你是否能正常回复群消息。请直接回复到飞书群里，就说：\\\"测试回复：我能正常收到和发送消息！\\\"\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1774111415993,\n      \"provenance\": {\n        \"kind\": \"inter_session\",\n        \"sourceSessionKey\": \"agent:main:feishu:group:oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e\",\n        \"sourceChannel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"sourceTool\": \"sessions_send\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"用户要求我直接回复到飞书群里，内容是：\\\"测试回复：我能正常收到和发送消息！\\\"\\n\\n我需要使用 message 工具发送消息到飞书群。根据上下文，当前频道是 feishu，群聊ID是 oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e。\\n\\n让我发送这条消息。\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"测试回复：我能正常收到和发送消息！\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"kimi-coding\",\n      \"model\": \"k2p5\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1774111415995\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"Agent-to-agent announce step.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"timestamp\": 1774111480426,\n      \"provenance\": {\n        \"kind\": \"inter_session\",\n        \"sourceSessionKey\": \"agent:main:feishu:group:oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e\",\n        \"sourceChannel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"sourceTool\": \"sessions_send\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"The user is testing if I can reply to group messages. The instruction says to reply directly to the Feishu group with: \\\"测试回复：我能正常收到和发送消息！\\\"\\n\\nThis is the final agent-to-agent announce step. I should reply with the requested message.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"测试回复：我能正常收到和发送消息！\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"kimi-coding\",\n      \"model\": \"k2p5\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1774111480427\n    }\n  ],\n  \"truncated\": true,\n  \"droppedMessages\": false,\n  \"contentTruncated\": true,\n  \"contentRedacted\": false,\n  \"bytes\": 4234\n}"}],"details":{"sessionKey":"agent:demo:feishu:group:oc_ad827e966bdde4ad7e375f74c2ba237e","messages":[{"role":